| HistoryText             = The '''Alpha-Males''' were [[Glossary:Clone|clones]] of [[Andrew Maguire (Earth-616)|Alpha]], a teenage boy who acquired extraordinary powers in an accident with [[Glossary:Parker Particles|Parker Particles]] at [[Horizon Labs (Location)|Horizon Labs]], created by the [[Miles Warren (Earth-616)|Jackal]] to mate his [[Spider Queens (Earth-616)|Spider Queens]] and make a powerful army under his control. However, the Alpha-Males didn't have any of Alpha's powers, as the accident that gave them to him didn't alter his DNA. The Alpha-Males were ultimately destroyed by Alpha when he managed to break free from the [[Carbonadium]] shackles the Jackal used to restrain him.{{r|Amazing Spider-Man Vol 1 693}}
